Date: 0/0/1982
Source: MAF Agricultural Glossary
Author: MAF
Vol / Page: 7
Edition:
Quote: Stock unit .. also referred to as ewe equivalent. It is the feed requirement used as the basis of comparison for different classes and species of stock. It expresses the annual feed requirements equivalent to one 55 kg ewe rearing a single lamb.
